Byte-by-byte Description of file: table1.dat
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
   Bytes Format Units     Label       Explanations
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
   1- 11  F11.6 0.1nm     Lambda      Vacuum wavelength
  13- 20  F8.6  0.1nm   e_Lambda      Uncertainty on wavelength
  22- 32  F11.5 cm-1      Wavenumber  Wavenumber (1/Lambda)
  34- 40  I7    ---       Intensity   Line peak intensity (in e^-^)
  42- 52  F11.6 0.1nm     preLambda   ? Previously-known wavelength
  55- 60  A6    ---       ID          Line identification (1)
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Note (1): ID as follows:
     ThI  = ThI from Palmer & Engleman (1983, Atlas of the Thorium spectrum)
     ThII = ThII from Palmer & Engleman (1983, Atlas of the Thorium spectrum)
    ThIII = ThIII from Palmer & Engleman (1983, Atlas of the Thorium spectrum)
     NoID = Not identified by Palmer & Engleman
            (1983, Atlas of the Thorium spectrum) (probably Th)
   Contam = Contaminant from Palmer & Engleman
            (1983, Atlas of the Thorium spectrum)
     ArI  = ArI from Norlen (1973PhyS....8..249N) and
            Whaling et al. (1995JQSRT..53....1W, 2002, JRES , 107, 149)
     ArII = ArII from Norlen (1973PhyS....8..249N) and
            Whaling et al. (1995JQSRT..53....1W, 2002, JRES, 107, 149)
        ? = Previously-unknown line
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

References:
